$ Oracle: Init parameter DIAGNOSTIC_DEST
@ diagnostic_desc

The parameter `diagnostic_desc` specifies the root directory of the → development/databases/Oracle/architecture/database/system-files/Automatic-Diagnostic-Repository[Automatic Diagnostic Repository],
ake the → development/databases/Oracle/architecture/database/system-files/Automatic-Diagnostic-Repository#oracle-adr-base[ADR base directory].

If `diagnostic_desc` is not set, the ADR root directory defaults to the location of the environment variable `ORACLE_BASE`.
-
If this variable is also not set, the location falls back to `→ Linux/fhs/u01/app/oracle/product/vv-v-v/dbhome_n[$ORACLE_HOME]/log`.

sa:
  → development/databases/Oracle/adminstration/init-parameters
